# Standard Environment Variables

## Port Configuration
- `WEB_PORT` (default 3206) — host port for web service (internal port 3206)
- `DB_HOST_PORT` (default 3207) — host port for database service (internal port 3207)
- `API_PORT` (default 3208) — host port for API service (internal port 3208)
- `REDIS_PORT` (default 3209) — host port for Redis service (internal port 3209)

## Application Configuration
- `APP_BASE_URL` — base URL used by tests/integrations
- `TZ` — timezone configuration
- `DB_CHARSET` — database character set
- `DB_COLLATION` — database collation

## Cleanup Configuration
- `CLEANUP_BEFORE_TESTS` (bool) — execute cleanup before tests
- `REMOVE_VOLUMES` (bool) — remove volumes during cleanup
- `CLEANUP_NETWORKS` (bool) — clean networks during cleanup

## Retry Configuration
- `RETRY_DELAY` — delay between retry attempts in seconds
- `MAX_RETRIES` — maximum retry attempts

## Timing Configuration
- `ENABLE_TIMING` — enable phase timing logging
- `TIMING_LOG_LEVEL` — timing log level
- `TIMING_LOG_RETENTION_DAYS` — timing log retention period

## Example Usage
```yaml
environment:
  WEB_PORT: "3206"
  DB_HOST_PORT: "3207"
  APP_BASE_URL: "http://localhost:3206"
  TZ: "UTC"
```
